.TH "gfs2_update_request_times" 9 "gfs2_update_request_times" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
gfs2_update_request_times \- Update locking statistics
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" gfs2_update_request_times
.BI "(struct gfs2_glock *gl "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "gl" 12
The glock to update
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
The irt (lock inter-request times) measures the average time
between requests to the dlm. It is updated immediately before
each dlm call.
